{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e7e0042e-4344-46a8-8fa9-ea7c95b9f745","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x switched the default test runner from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP).**\n\nBecause MTP is now the default, `vstest.console.exe` can no longer discover or run your tests — the test host no longer exposes the VSTest adapter entry point.\n\n### Options to fix\n\n1. **Migrate your CI to `dotnet test`** (recommended — it works with MTP out of the box in SDK 4.x):\n   ```\n   dotnet test MyTests.csproj\n   ```\n\n2. **Opt back into VSTest** if you must keep `vstest.console`:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- In your .csproj or Directory.Build.props -->\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\nThis property restores the VSTest adapter wiring and makes `vstest.console` work again, but you lose the new MTP features (parallel execution, hang detection, etc.).","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"a826a17c-359c-4bc1-ab3c-a82f0a597399","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a breaking change when upgrading from MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0 to MSTest.Sdk/4.1.0, specifically related to test discovery with vstest.console. This is a knowledge question about MSTest SDK changes, not a code modification task.\n\nLet me look at the files in the current directory to see if there's relevant context, but this is likely a question I can answer from knowledge about MSTest SDK changes.\n\nThe key change: Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.8 (or around that version), Microsoft introduced the \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\" (MTP) as the new test runner. \n\nIn version 4.0 and later, MTP became the default runner instead of VSTest, which means projects no longer generate VSTest-compatible test hosts by default—that's why `vstest.console` can't discover tests anymore. To fix this, you'd either need to switch to `dotnet test` which works with MTP, or configure the project to use VSTest as the test platform instead.\n\nLet me look at the project files to see what's actually configured.","outputTokens":618,"requestId":"BC22:223B6B:225DBEA:2654DA6:69FAABE7"},"id":"a46c1bef-e94e-4b47-af74-375055d43658","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:48:21.195Z","parentId":"671692ba-a1fa-4beb-9b38-2633623c6f6e"}
